(71, '4064', 1442, 'JOSE', 'JIMENEZ', 'joseajimenez@me.com', '7328903920', 'DJIiOSCombo1', 'DJI MINI IOSD', 1, 0, 4, 'Hello!\r\n\r\nI hoep all is well. I ams ending this email as it was suggested by one of the operators on your website. On 11/01/13 I purchased a few things from you guys one of them being a DJI mini iOSD. I have used it about 10 times since and it has worked great. Except two days ago it stopped working completely. The lights turn on fine and blink which means it has communication with whatever is plugged in and still no go. I just received my second DJI Mini iOSD which is for my S800 and if I just grab the mini iOSD and connect the cable I have already wired it works, but the old one just doesnt work. Again light blinks but still no go. I removed it off my rig that I have never crashed and connected it to the computer and it picks it up fine as well. If it could be fixed or replaced that would be so great.\r\n\r\nThank you!', '2013-12-11 16:31:46', '2014-01-13 13:38:15'),
