(75, '0', 0, 'brandon', 'loska', 'bloska@perfectshotproductions.com', '7023244802', 'futaba 8fs', '', 1, 0, 4, 'I have had the S800 eve since mid sept.  For some reason the futaba 8fg has lost connection to the receiver, it will not turn on with the correct stick position, also the switches are not working for some reason.  I have spoken with you tech department yesterday &amp; today.  I was instructed by them to send the transmitter to intelligent uas, then upon receiving, you would reprogram my transmitter &amp; mail back to me asap. \r\nthank you.', '2013-12-24 12:57:33', '2014-01-02 17:20:14'),
