(79, '0', 0, 'Andrew', 'Smith', 'andrew@smpwebvideo.com', '610-918-9811', 'DJI Phantom', '', 1, 0, 4, 'Included Items:\r\nDJI Phantom V1 with Upgrade Kit for ZenMuse\r\nFatshark FPV transmitter and upgraded antenna\r\nCustomer FPV to Go Pro Hero USB to FPV cable\r\nAll allen screws are in battery compartment and kept exterior screws installed to save reassembly time for me :-)\r\n\r\nRepair Request Instructions: \r\nMotor Upgrade:\r\nUpgrade my motors to the T-Motor Anti-Gravity Motors\r\nCheck my front Left ESC as it is probably not fixable ? Lost the original pad while soldering,\r\nplease test other ESC''s \r\n\r\nFPV Optimization:\r\nCan you please make my fatshark transmitter more elegant in terms of the power connection  as well mounting it to the copter. My solution was pretty bad :-)\r\n\r\nI am using the GoPro Black and ZenMuse combination. Can you recommend a better cable to connect directly to my GoPro versus my custom FPV cable ?\r\n\r\nContact Information:\r\nAndrew Smith\r\n316 Joseph Drive\r\nWest Chester, PA 19380\r\nPhone 610-357-9444\r\nemail: Andrew@smpwebvideo.com\r\n\r\nPlease let me know if you have any questions. \r\n\r\nThanks,\r\n\r\nAndrew\r\n', '2014-01-07 14:32:45', '2014-01-23 14:59:43'),
