(87, '0', 0, 'Brett', 'Lockwood', 'lockwoodbrett@gmail.com', '803-261-6805', 'DJI NAZA M V2', '', 1, 0, 7, 'Good afternoon,\r\nI would like to send in my Naza FC unit for possible repair. A hard crash into a stream has caused irregular flight control. I have tested the control unit to the best of my ability by replacing the ESCs, motors, transmitter and receiver, PMU and full recalibration. The craft will not hold a steady course in any flight mode.\r\n\r\nThank you,\r\nBrett Lockwood', '2014-01-13 13:07:35', '2014-10-29 12:03:05'),
