(90, '4466', 0, 'Alex', 'Ristanovic', 'alex@simplylogical.com', '630-204-2219', 'DJI Phantom 2 Vision', 'DJI-Phantom-II-Vision', 1, 0, 4, 'This unit made an electronic screeching noise from the gimbal/servo unit from the camera. I was meaning to warranty repair this but it was operating normally. However, I had an accident not with it and it looks like that very same piece needs to be addressed. The servo works, however the camera won''t move because the servo gear seems to not make contact with the inside of the camera housing properly. It seems a piece has come off, it may be something simple. I do however want the gimbal replaced because the screeching noise is consistent and loud, it happens whether you are adjusting the tilt of the camera or if it''s just sitting idle and not flying. It''s been like that since I''ve had this. It may also resolve the problem I''m having with the camera not attaching correctly anymore. Call to discuss. Thanks', '2014-01-22 20:48:52', '2014-02-28 10:51:29'),
