(127, '0', 0, 'Bart', 'Johnson', 'bart@bartjohnsonproductions.com', '9123983333', 'DJI Phantom', '', 1, 0, 4, 'I have a DJI Phantom V1.1.1 that is in need of some servicing and perhaps repair.  The Phantom recently had a crash and was submerged in water for almost 20 seconds.  I was able to retrieve the Phantom and quickly dry it and all of its components out.  After completely drying, the Phantom appeared to be operating normally.  Recently the Phantom has developed an issue.  When it is powered on, it continuously flashes yellow, indicating it cannot pair with the transmitter.  I have tried binding the Phantom and the transmitter, but have not had any luck.  I even replaced the receiver board in the Phantom and attempted binding again.  I would like to have this issue looked into, as well as have the rest of the Phantom''s functions inspected to make sure being submerged has not caused any other hidden damage.  Thank you.', '2014-04-07 16:36:11', '2014-04-21 09:19:03'),
