(131, '0', 0, 'Bill', 'Frischling', 'bill@frischling.com', '703-623-1424', 'DJI Phantom Vision 2', '', 1, 0, 7, 'Hello...\r\n\r\nI have a DJI Phantom Vision 2. Had a couple of rough crashes, and after this last one, it appears the switch within the ball camera snapped off. It does not power up. The drone still flies (very carefully), but there''s no power from the WiFi or the camera. A small piece is rattling inside that appears to be the switch on the board under the large button.\r\n\r\nI''m looking to have that piece repaired. I can send in the whole system with remote to be safe. Note the system is all the original RTF system, however the WiFi range extender has been modded to take a booster antennae. That is on the remote and is not affected by the crash.', '2014-04-14 13:46:51', '2014-10-29 12:05:00'),
