(136, '0', 0, 'Stan', 'Preston', 'preston@prestonproductions.net', '410-683-0000', 'DJI Phantom 1.1', '', 1, 0, 7, 'Hi,\r\n\r\nI purchased this DJI phantom from another dealer and I''m hoping you can do some service. Specifically I''m hoping you can install the DJI 5.8 GHZ Video Link that is enclosed in the unit. I may also be interested in purchasing a monitor to work with the Video Link and would appreciate your recommendation and cost for that.\r\n\r\nSecondly, I crashed the phantom and need the mounting plate on the gimbal to be replaced along with the cable that connects to the gimbal from the phantom. Once received, please inspect the unit to confirm this is the only damage and that it should operate properly after these repairs. Please provide an estimate for these services and feel free to contact me with any questions or concerns. I will be shipping the unit to you via Fed Ex.\r\n\r\nThanks for your help,\r\n\r\nStan Preston\r\n410.683.0000', '2014-04-22 10:22:52', '2014-10-29 12:06:15'),
