(149, '0', 2157, 'Robert', 'Dodd', 'projects@txpromomedia.com', '9037076761', 'DJI z-15 prof camera mount gimbal sony nex 5 nex 7 version', '330769108709', 1, 0, 7, 'Was working great but has developed an issue of jitter on the pitch axis. Notice when you spin the gimbal on its pitch axis there is some friction through a portion of its travel. This Gimbal has been flown approx 10 times and has never been in a crash or hard landing. Had it mounted on an S1000 with the sony nex5n camera (using the adapter plate supplied for the nex 5) Not sure what is the issue. Have purchased another unit from you through your website so I can continue to work while this is getting resolved. The unit I am sending back was purchased from you through Ebay item#221249987911.\r\n\r\nI spoke with tech dept a few days ago about this issue. So they should be aware. If at all possible I would like it repaired or refund of purchase price. Again I have already purchased another unit from you guys while this is being resolved. \r\n\r\nThank you for your help with this matter and please call me with any questions. 903-707-6761', '2014-05-03 10:53:59', '2014-10-29 12:01:28'),
