(161, '0', 0, 'Mark', 'Mai', 'Mark@graywolfci.com', '888-364-0529', 'Phantom Vision Plus', '', 1, 0, 4, 'I crashed the unit from about 50 feet up. The landing gear and one prop and prop guard took a brunt of the hit, but since the accident the gimbal is not working and keeps flipping around and the camera does not connect to my Iphone. I flew 2 batteries through it and it appears to be flying fine. I would like the gimbal fixed and also the unit tested to insure its working properly. I will fedex the unit in its case to you tomorrow. Please let me know how soon I can expect it back as I have an inspection to do next weekend in Florida and am hoping it can be repaired by then. Please be advised when repaired I would like the unit overnighted back. I will incur the charges for this.\r\n\r\nThank you so much!', '2014-05-27 20:26:31', '2014-06-05 10:23:40'),
