(165, '0', 0, 'Chris', 'Titus', 'ctitus@optonline.net', '2032470063', 'DJI S800', '', 1, 0, 4, 'Crashed unit and will need two new arms as well as any other parts you find were damaged. ', '2014-05-29 14:53:12', '2014-06-12 12:34:40'),
(166, '8072', 0, 'Edward', 'Gordon', 'nedgordon@mac.com', '617-838-5000', 'gimbal &amp; camrea -phantom', 'DJI-Phantom-II-Vision-plus-one-xtra', 1, 0, 2, 'After several flights, the gimbal is no longer working properly. When connected and powered it does a constant crazy dance. I have enclosed the gimbal and camera.', '2014-06-03 12:38:29', '2014-06-03 12:38:29'),
(167, '0', 0, 'Dave ', 'Dodds', 'davedodds@me.com', '703-862-7421', 'Zenmuse H3-3D Gimbal ', '', 1, 0, 4, 'Gimbal was involved in a crash. After the crash, the pitch or tilt motor finds it difficult to maintain position after initialization. Specifically, the pitch motor moves back and forth and vibrates during this movement.', '2014-06-03 12:56:25', '2014-09-04 09:11:13'),
(168, '0', 0, 'Alex', 'Dolce', 'whereisdolce@gmail.com', '2014079210', 'phantom', '', 1, 0, 4, 'Hello,\r\n\r\nI would like the gimbal and the video transmitter installed as well was as have the skyzone goggles set up. It took a nasty hit and I would also like phantom itself checked out for any damage.\r\n\r\nBest\r\n-Alex Dolce', '2014-06-03 14:36:33', '2014-06-04 16:25:27'),
(169, '0', 0, 'art', 'sribanpot', 'artsribanpot@comcast.net', '8609650183', 'dji phantom 2 vision plus', '', 0, 0, 2, 'My phantom 2 vision plus''gimbal is not level. It was working fine for many days and then suddenly last week gimbal does not point the camera at the horizontal level.', '2014-06-05 10:24:23', '2014-06-05 10:24:23'),
