(171, '5373', 0, 'Vladimir', 'Mirkovich', 'vladmirkovich@gmail.com', '248.891.8523', 'Vision 2', 'PV 330', 1, 0, 4, 'The unit was calibrated before every flight. I had more than 20 flights since purchased with no major issues.\r\nOn April 7,2014 the copter started the flight with calibrated compass and 11 satellites. It was flying fine for a minute or so and then just started getting out of control and simply flew away. I searched it for hours but had no luck.\r\n\r\nMeanwhile I contacted Katie Tran and Pierre who offered me a new unit for half the price.\r\n\r\ntwo days ago I ran into my neighbor who luckily fount the copter in his yard. I tried to power it up and check the firmware but if would not register the compass or GPS function.\r\n\r\nPlease repair or replace the unit under the warranty. I may be interested in upgrading as I don''t want to lose it again.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nVladimir Mirkovich\r\n ', '2014-06-07 15:54:41', '2014-07-14 15:11:11'),
(172, '0', 986, 'peter', 'ellin', 'peter@tinycars.biz', '631-782-8805', 'PHANTOM VISION', '', 1, 0, 2, 'CUSTOMER HIT TREE AND VISION FELL IN FRESHWATER LAKE. STAYED IN WATER FOR 10 MINUTES. HE FOUND IT TOOK IT HOME AND TURNED IT ON. SMELLED BURNING PLASTIC AND THE LIGHTS FLASHED OUT. THEN HE PUT IT IN RICE FOR 3 DAYS\r\n\r\nPLEASE DO COMPLETE DIAGNOSTIC AND QUOTE ME FOR REPAIRS. CHECK EVERYTHING INCL CAMERA.\r\n\r\nCALL ME WITH RESULTS.\r\n\r\nPETER', '2014-06-09 09:43:02', '2014-06-09 09:43:02'),
(173, '0', 0, 'Ryan', 'Kim', 'ryankim1029@gmail.com', '703-673-6415', 'Phantom 2 with H3-2D', '', 1, 0, 7, '3 of the four motors are not freely spinning. ', '2014-06-10 10:51:39', '2014-10-28 14:05:11'),
