(198, '0', 0, 'Michael', 'Hammitt', 'mtspot@charter.net', '715-223-5916', 'DJI Phantom Vistion 2+', '', 1, 0, 4, 'Problem #1:  Micro-USB charging port on Wi-Fi extender appears to be broken.\r\n\r\nProblem #2:  Camera port/mSD card does not appear to be working.  Will not establish a link with my PC.  Cannot access pictures from DJI app either.\r\n\r\nI just received this last week from your company.  Called tech support concerning this issue.  This is a full-warranty repair.', '2014-07-01 09:24:16', '2014-07-07 16:31:32'),
