(203, '0', 0, 'Andrew', 'Ryback', 'aryback@broadcastmgmt.com', '202.683.4162', 'DJI Phantom 2 Vision+', '', 1, 0, 4, 'Our company owns a DJI Phantom 2 Vision+ that was recently damaged in a crash.  One of the arms is slightly bent or askew, so the blade hits the body of the drone when it''s turned on.  There also appears to be a piece on the gimbal that''s broken as well.  We''d like to have both issues repaired.', '2014-07-07 12:02:49', '2014-08-28 10:44:29');
