(292, '0', 0, 'FELIPE', 'PRADO DIAZ', 'fprado@me.com', '5255-52800068', 'ZENMUSE', '', 1, 0, 2, 'I have a Dji S 800 with a Zenmuse for Sony Nex5 that needs repair. The problem seams to be that when you move the camera to make a 360 degree turn when it goes around 180 degrees losses te horizontal level turning into the right a little bit. The other problem it has is when you are turning the zenmuse not always but sometimes it jumps a little. I know this two errors are not a big deal but it is not working properly or as it should be.\r\nI took the zenmuse with Heliboss which is a Dji representative office an sales office for México and Central América. they told me that they were join to send it to China, BUT they are having problems with China, they are receiving things they sent to repair and they are receiving back with out been repair after 3 months ! they tell me that they can not guarantee that they will receive it as it should. So my question is Can you repair it? I am already a customer form you, I been ordering a few things I can´t get in México and I wonder if you can help me in this case.\r\n\r\nI use this equipment to fil locations, hotels, and golf courses so it is importa for me to have it in the best condition and confident always.\r\n\r\nIf you can repair this zenmuse,  I will send it, wait for the inspection and price to pay for repair, I will pay you in advance with paypal and also the amount to be paid to resend it to México City.\r\n\r\nThank you very much for your kind help.\r\nBest regards, Felipe Prado.', '2014-09-30 17:02:13', '2014-09-30 17:02:13'),
