(573, 228, 3, 1, 'Received P2V+ with:\n\nP2 Bat, \nGimbal P2V+;\nTX with AA bat;\n4 pairs of props;\nExtra battery;\n\nWe checked the P2V+:\n\n- At first the radio was mess up ; We use RC system to calibrate the radio again. Now the Phantom can starts its motors. We will not take labor fee on this.\n\n- Checked FPV: Gimbal works : can keep position and correct motion. However, no FPV from the Vision Plus, cannot access the SD card, take picture, read craft infor; The Wifi Transmitter inside the Phantom 2 V+ could be bad already. Do you want us to fix the FPV? If not, then you can pay shipping fee, and get this one back.\n\nHave a good day.\n\n\nUpdated by: Nguyen Tina', '2014-08-13 15:20:04'),
